Let’s propagate some lavender 🪻
- find non flowering stems
- cut where it starts to get woody
- peel off most leaves
- cut stem at a leaf nub near bottom
- place in well draining potting mix 
- keep moist, but don’t overwater
- place in non direct sunlight
🌤️🌤️🌤️🌤️🌤️
Save if you need to replace your woody lavender, or want to grow some more indoors over the fall and water seasons

#propagation #propogatingplants #lavender #gardening #houstongardening #woodylavender
